                <div itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject">
            <meta itemprop="url" content="https://www.uni-europa.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Opening-soon-William-Murphy-flickr-with-comment-1024x576.png">
